songs.lyrics:
[Female on answering machine]
Listen, muthafucka
I’m playin’ your goddamn new muthafuckin’ record
And you got these muthafuckin’ kids runnin’ around here
12 muthafuckin’ kids on my welfare and you makin’ muthafuckin’ hits
Listen, muthafucka, A-M-Jason-muthafuckin’-G
You know to come in this muthafucka and take care of these goddamn kids
songs.title: My Ho, My Kids
